parameters.name: AuthIds
parameters.description: The unique ID of the AccessKey pair.

parameters.name: Lang
parameters.description:
The language of the content within the request and response. Default value: **zh**. Valid values:

*   **zh**: Chinese
*   **en**: English

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Default value: 20.

parameters.name: Status
parameters.description:
The status of the AccessKey pair. Valid values:

*   **0**: enabled
*   **1**: disabled

parameters.name: SubAccountName
parameters.description: The username of the sub-account of the cloud service provider to which the AccessKey pair belongs.

parameters.name: VendorAuthAlias
parameters.description: The name of the AccessKey pair.
